        "timestamp": "2019-01-18 13:57:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nthis change contradicts the approach that we use in ONAP for bringing the onap-dcae-dcaepolicy-lib.  \n\nThe agreement is that we do not change the API on the lib and docker/k8s plugins have the range for the version <3.0.0.  That allows us to have the lib hosted on public pypi and not to have the tsunami of plugin versions spreading through the blueprints in ONAP.  \n\nPlease abandon",
        "patchset_number": 1
